WEBVTT

01:30.910 --> 01:35.020
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.729 --> 01:39.310
[2020]

01:38.840 --> 01:39.430
Xiaolan.

01:40.120 --> 01:40.870
Take this contract

01:40.870 --> 01:42.270
to Finance for stamping.

01:48.150 --> 01:48.710
Ms. Liu,

01:48.840 --> 01:49.789
Legal hasn't finished

01:49.789 --> 01:51.560
reviewing this contract yet, right?

01:51.560 --> 01:52.690
This is a rush order.

01:53.280 --> 01:55.039
It takes Legal 3 whole days
to review a contract.

01:55.039 --> 01:56.370
We can't wait that long.

01:57.840 --> 01:58.590
Fine, fine.

01:58.840 --> 02:00.100
I can't get you to work.

02:01.480 --> 02:02.610
I'll go do it myself.

02:10.910 --> 02:11.800
During the interview,

02:11.800 --> 02:12.630
didn't you say you were

02:12.630 --> 02:14.800
the top sales champion
at your last company?

02:14.800 --> 02:15.930
Why are you so rigid?

02:16.520 --> 02:18.120
If you keep being this timid,

02:18.520 --> 02:20.980
don't blame others
for stealing your deals.

02:21.520 --> 02:22.450
Watch and learn.

02:41.670 --> 02:44.700
[Episode 30 An ounce of prevention is
worth a pound of cure]

02:49.000 --> 02:51.460
[Chengrong Electronics City
Big Sale for Opening]

03:07.000 --> 03:09.310
Open the doors for business!

03:09.310 --> 03:10.120
Got it!

03:11.310 --> 03:12.960
Yes!

03:13.340 --> 03:16.630
[Chengrong Electronics City]

03:54.560 --> 03:55.870
One hundred... one hundred yuan!

03:55.870 --> 03:56.800
One hundred yuan today!

03:56.800 --> 03:57.190
Here.

04:20.269 --> 04:21.120
Here you are.

04:28.920 --> 04:29.560
Mr. Du,

04:29.870 --> 04:31.070
business is booming.

04:31.120 --> 04:32.190
You're finally here!

04:32.190 --> 04:33.520
Now that you're here...

04:35.159 --> 04:36.480
I feel at ease since you're here.

04:36.480 --> 04:37.740
But why is he here, too?

04:38.600 --> 04:39.190
Ms. Xia is

04:39.190 --> 04:40.850
a major client of our law firm.

04:40.870 --> 04:43.159
For the next few days,
on behalf of our law firm,

04:43.159 --> 04:44.159
I will be accompanying Ms. Xia

04:44.159 --> 04:45.950
to handle the work
at the Electronics City.

04:45.950 --> 04:46.750
Any problem?

04:48.680 --> 04:49.280
Of course,

04:50.040 --> 04:51.170
we are also glad to be

04:51.430 --> 04:52.830
of service to you, Mr. Du.

04:54.040 --> 04:54.510
Mr. Du,

04:54.720 --> 04:55.480
have you got the vehicles

04:55.480 --> 04:56.680
I asked you to prepare?

04:56.680 --> 04:57.610
They're all set.

04:58.070 --> 04:58.430
Good.

04:58.830 --> 04:59.600
Then arrange for them

04:59.600 --> 05:00.830
to parade across the city.

05:00.830 --> 05:01.310
Hua,

05:01.630 --> 05:02.490
make it happen.

05:02.560 --> 05:03.190
On it!

05:09.680 --> 05:11.430
Good news! Good news!

05:11.680 --> 05:13.240
Chengrong Electronics City Plaza is

05:13.240 --> 05:15.070
having a big sale for its opening!

05:15.070 --> 05:16.870
Spend over 100 yuan

05:17.160 --> 05:19.950
and get your receipt
to enter a lucky draw!

05:20.750 --> 05:22.080
One first-prize winner

05:22.120 --> 05:23.450
will get a brand new car!

05:23.660 --> 05:27.470
♪ The sunlight fell on me ♪

05:24.000 --> 05:25.460
Two second-prize winners

05:25.630 --> 05:27.160
will each get a motorcycle!

05:27.430 --> 05:29.070
One hundred third-prize winners
will each get

05:28.740 --> 05:31.220
♪ And sets my heart ablaze ♪

05:29.480 --> 05:30.070
a Wenquxing Electronic Dictionary!

05:30.070 --> 05:30.830
What is this Electronics City?

05:30.830 --> 05:32.010
They're going all out
with the advertising!

05:32.010 --> 05:34.310
♪ Are you also the same? ♪

05:32.040 --> 05:32.920
A car raffle?

05:32.920 --> 05:33.560
For real?

05:33.630 --> 05:34.800
We can go and find out for ourselves.

05:34.800 --> 05:35.870
Chengrong Electronics City Plaza is

05:35.870 --> 05:37.120
celebrating its grand opening!

05:37.120 --> 05:38.480
Free shuttle bus!

05:37.130 --> 05:40.750
♪ Dreams will always shine ♪

05:38.600 --> 05:40.390
Free direct shuttle!

05:41.040 --> 05:41.830
Hello.

05:42.190 --> 05:44.000
Free direct shuttle!

05:42.260 --> 05:44.690
♪ There may also be regrets ♪

05:44.390 --> 05:45.240
The third prize!

05:44.720 --> 05:48.210
♪ If you lose something,
be strong ♪

05:45.270 --> 05:46.720
You won the third prize!

05:46.750 --> 05:48.720
A Wenquxing device for you!

05:49.030 --> 05:51.170
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

05:52.370 --> 05:54.940
♪ The dreams we dream in the day time ♪

05:55.780 --> 05:58.190
♪ Is passionate yet naive ♪

05:58.909 --> 06:03.790
♪ Our youth ♪

06:03.810 --> 06:07.340
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

06:07.360 --> 06:10.740
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

06:10.920 --> 06:13.760
♪ We never give up ♪

06:11.190 --> 06:12.390
It's the third prize!

06:12.480 --> 06:13.680
I won the third prize!

06:14.190 --> 06:15.430
I won the third prize!

06:14.380 --> 06:17.600
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

06:16.920 --> 06:19.040
I won a prize!

06:17.620 --> 06:20.850
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

06:20.360 --> 06:22.240
I only spent 100 yuan,

06:20.880 --> 06:24.270
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

06:22.240 --> 06:23.360
and I won a prize!

06:23.480 --> 06:25.510
Everyone, just go shopping!

06:24.300 --> 06:27.350
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

06:27.360 --> 06:28.360
Look, everyone!

06:27.570 --> 06:30.790
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

06:28.390 --> 06:30.160
Congratulations to this gentleman!

06:30.160 --> 06:31.120
Hongxia, hurry up.

06:30.810 --> 06:34.040
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

06:31.600 --> 06:32.400
Hurry, hurry.

06:32.600 --> 06:33.060
Come on.

06:33.310 --> 06:34.040
I won

06:34.040 --> 06:36.190
this third prize, which is worth

06:34.070 --> 06:37.460
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

06:36.190 --> 06:36.870
499 yuan.

06:37.040 --> 06:37.630
Later,

06:37.490 --> 06:40.540
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

06:37.800 --> 06:39.240
I'll go buy more stuff

06:39.560 --> 06:40.040
because

06:40.040 --> 06:41.720
I've got my eye on this car.

06:41.010 --> 06:43.950
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

06:43.830 --> 06:45.000
There's really someone who won a prize!

06:44.320 --> 06:50.300
♪ That'd be enough ♪

06:45.510 --> 06:46.040
Mother!

06:46.630 --> 06:47.920
Let's bring the box lunches
over here for sale!

06:47.920 --> 06:48.560
Okay, let's go.

06:48.560 --> 06:49.920
Don't push. No crowding.

06:49.920 --> 06:52.159
The big prizes are yet to come!

06:54.560 --> 06:56.290
What is this Wenquxing anyway?

06:56.480 --> 06:59.080
Why do I have to promote it
through a lucky draw?

06:59.190 --> 07:00.520
Do you have shares in it?

07:00.800 --> 07:01.270
Yes, I do.

07:01.270 --> 07:02.510
I'm its original shareholder.

07:02.510 --> 07:03.970
Mr. Du, please support us.

07:04.040 --> 07:04.970
Are you serious?

07:05.390 --> 07:06.800
You've even invested in this?

07:06.800 --> 07:07.800
Is it profitable?

07:08.030 --> 07:09.510
This thing is for learning English.

07:09.510 --> 07:11.210
It'll go viral for quite a while.

07:11.210 --> 07:12.610
Promoting it is worth it.

07:16.040 --> 07:16.440
Mr. Du,

07:16.920 --> 07:17.560
they have already drawn

07:17.560 --> 07:18.690
500 raffle tickets.

07:19.000 --> 07:20.260
Okay, get back to work.

07:21.040 --> 07:22.300
It's only been an hour.

07:25.240 --> 07:26.740
Five hundred raffle tickets

07:26.740 --> 07:28.420
mean 50,000 yuan in sales.

07:28.680 --> 07:30.000
We just opened for business.

07:30.000 --> 07:30.830
The sales peak is usually

07:30.830 --> 07:32.430
around noon and in the afternoon.

07:32.430 --> 07:33.800
It looks like the 1.5 million

07:33.800 --> 07:35.730
daily sales target is achievable.

07:36.600 --> 07:37.360
Du Zhaoji is

07:38.040 --> 07:38.900
doomed to lose.

07:39.480 --> 07:41.920
He'll lose his shirt.

07:46.200 --> 07:48.280
Come and take a look! Hot box lunches!

07:48.310 --> 07:49.750
Come and see what you want!

07:49.750 --> 07:51.190
We have both meat and vegetables.

07:51.190 --> 07:53.480
It's the second prize, a motorcycle!

07:55.640 --> 07:56.620
Congratulations!

07:56.620 --> 07:57.890
This is our opening's

07:57.920 --> 08:00.310
very first motorcycle giveaway.

08:00.310 --> 08:02.120
Even this guy could win a motorcycle!

08:02.120 --> 08:02.510
You know what?

08:02.510 --> 08:03.870
If I went to draw,

08:04.040 --> 08:04.560
that car surely

08:04.560 --> 08:05.360
wouldn't be mine either.

08:05.360 --> 08:06.070
Cut the crap.

08:06.070 --> 08:06.720
Just hurry up

08:06.720 --> 08:07.830
and serve the rice. Come on.

08:07.830 --> 08:08.390
Here, give me one.

08:08.390 --> 08:09.040
Listen,

08:09.360 --> 08:10.800
we need Junbao to deliver another load.

08:10.800 --> 08:12.190
Five hundred portions
surely won't be enough today.

08:12.190 --> 08:13.720
Everyone in Shengcheng is here.

08:13.720 --> 08:14.120
Got it!

08:19.270 --> 08:21.240
We've got a motorcycle winner!

08:21.310 --> 08:22.600
Congratulations!

08:23.000 --> 08:23.730
Xia Xiaolan,

08:24.120 --> 08:24.920
what on earth is

08:24.920 --> 08:25.870
inside your brain?

08:25.870 --> 08:27.040
These marketing tactics

08:27.040 --> 08:28.240
work so effectively!

08:28.260 --> 08:29.800
Why are you so good at reading people

08:29.800 --> 08:30.910
and influencing them?

08:30.910 --> 08:32.470
It will only get more and more crowded.

08:32.470 --> 08:33.510
Regarding security and order,

08:33.510 --> 08:34.669
we must keep a close eye on it.

08:34.669 --> 08:36.510
If a stampede happens,

08:36.669 --> 08:37.510
today's great coup

08:37.510 --> 08:38.640
will all go to waste.

08:39.120 --> 08:39.510
Hua.

08:39.970 --> 08:40.909
Have you contacted

08:40.909 --> 08:42.039
the city officials?

08:42.080 --> 08:42.600
How's it?

08:42.600 --> 08:44.000
They are sending more staff.

08:44.000 --> 08:45.080
It looks like

08:45.080 --> 08:46.960
everything is under control.

08:48.120 --> 08:48.960
We still need to be careful

08:48.960 --> 08:50.120
in case someone incites the crowd

08:50.120 --> 08:50.980
to cause chaos.

08:52.150 --> 08:52.750
By the way,

08:52.810 --> 08:53.930
add two more

08:53.950 --> 08:54.880
free tea stands.

08:55.200 --> 08:57.230
People can skip a meal for entertainment,

08:57.230 --> 08:58.890
but they can't go dehydrated.

08:58.960 --> 09:00.360
I'll get on it right away.

09:01.000 --> 09:02.360
You guys should eat, too.

09:02.360 --> 09:03.030
Have some food.

09:03.030 --> 09:03.490
Come on.

09:05.320 --> 09:05.760
Here you are.

09:05.760 --> 09:06.360
Thank you.

09:06.790 --> 09:07.990
Be careful, it's hot.

09:08.870 --> 09:09.390
Here you go.

09:09.390 --> 09:09.850
Thanks.

09:10.030 --> 09:12.030
Those in line, please wait a moment.

09:22.600 --> 09:23.720
1.71 million.

09:25.910 --> 09:26.510
Get back to work.

09:26.510 --> 09:27.240
Okay, Mr. Du.

09:33.240 --> 09:33.640
Hello?

09:34.030 --> 09:34.560
Xiaolan,

09:34.790 --> 09:35.590
you know what?

09:35.600 --> 09:36.960
It's 1.71 million!

09:37.240 --> 09:38.480
Our first day's turnover

09:38.480 --> 09:39.720
already reached 1.71 million.

09:39.720 --> 09:41.240
Everyone loves this model.

09:41.240 --> 09:42.100
Can we continue

09:42.360 --> 09:44.030
the shopping lottery tomorrow?

09:44.030 --> 09:44.510
Yes.

09:44.600 --> 09:45.750
Just as I said,

09:45.790 --> 09:47.270
we'll run it for 3 days straight.

09:47.270 --> 09:47.670
Okay.

09:50.840 --> 09:51.550
I bet you,

09:51.790 --> 09:52.850
he'd brag to his dad

09:52.960 --> 09:54.390
the moment he hung up.

09:56.510 --> 09:57.000
Hello?

09:57.600 --> 09:58.150
Dad.

09:58.800 --> 10:00.060
I want to report to you.

10:00.080 --> 10:01.320
Our Chengrong Plaza's turnover

10:01.320 --> 10:02.360
for the first day was

10:02.360 --> 10:03.360
1.71 million.

10:04.390 --> 10:06.450
I know. You don't need to report to me.

10:07.320 --> 10:09.120
Bring me the account book tomorrow

10:09.120 --> 10:10.520
at the birthday banquet.

10:14.200 --> 10:15.320
Damn Old Man.

10:18.670 --> 10:19.600
Passive smoke is

10:19.600 --> 10:21.120
harmful to the baby.

10:25.870 --> 10:28.030
That was Zhaohui on the phone.

10:29.260 --> 10:30.170
The Chengrong Plaza

10:30.170 --> 10:32.920
that he built

10:33.010 --> 10:34.120
just opened for business.

10:34.120 --> 10:35.450
It's off to a good start.

10:36.000 --> 10:37.000
What do you think?

10:38.270 --> 10:39.000
Me?

10:39.750 --> 10:41.210
What opinion could I have?

10:42.030 --> 10:44.150
No matter who wins or loses between them,

10:44.150 --> 10:45.080
aren't you still

10:45.150 --> 10:47.010
the one calling the shots, Mr. Du?

10:47.200 --> 10:48.400
As long as you love me,

10:48.910 --> 10:49.670
I don't care about

10:49.670 --> 10:50.800
those messy things.

10:51.550 --> 10:52.390
Second Young Master,

10:52.390 --> 10:54.720
here is the data for the Electronics City.

11:05.080 --> 11:05.910
Du Zhaohui,

11:06.600 --> 11:08.400
I'll let you gloat for a few days.

11:09.270 --> 11:10.200
Your luck won't

11:10.200 --> 11:11.000
last forever.

11:12.700 --> 11:15.190
[Day 2 of the Electronics City's opening]

11:26.170 --> 11:28.750
♪ It'll be dark in a minute ♪

11:29.240 --> 11:31.760
♪ Don't rush to success ♪

11:33.230 --> 11:35.380
♪ Time flies so fast like lightning ♪

11:36.510 --> 11:38.510
♪ If you want to be happy,
get out on the streets ♪

11:40.040 --> 11:42.570
♪ No need to turn down the volume ♪

11:43.220 --> 11:45.820
♪ The lamps sway gently in the wind
at dusk ♪

11:46.480 --> 11:49.530
♪ My little beige headphones
blink in comfort ♪

11:49.120 --> 11:50.270
So lucky!

11:50.550 --> 11:51.480
Box lunches for sale!

11:50.770 --> 11:52.710
♪ My legs just won't stay still ♪

11:51.550 --> 11:53.030
Two yuan each.

11:53.120 --> 11:54.670
Two meat and two vegetable dishes.

11:54.670 --> 11:55.200
Okay.

11:55.390 --> 11:56.840
♪ Tomorrow seems so far away ♪

11:55.480 --> 11:55.840
Here.

11:55.840 --> 11:57.200
Please help yourself to chopsticks.

11:57.200 --> 11:58.860
♪ The world keeps spinning ♪

11:57.390 --> 11:59.080
Box lunches here!

11:59.200 --> 11:59.670
Here.

11:59.220 --> 12:01.730
♪ Do you wanna dance tonight? ♪

11:59.670 --> 12:01.270
Why are Junshan and Junbao
still not here?

12:01.270 --> 12:02.600
They're poaching our customers.

12:02.200 --> 12:03.990
♪ Tomorrow seems so far away ♪

12:02.670 --> 12:03.240
Exactly.

12:03.240 --> 12:04.120
Coming. Which dishes do you want?

12:04.020 --> 12:05.580
♪ Everything is spinning ♪

12:04.120 --> 12:05.720
Free rice refills

12:05.750 --> 12:06.800
for you to eat your fill!

12:06.010 --> 12:09.120
♪ Do you wanna dance tonight? ♪

12:07.080 --> 12:08.510
Come on, get in line.

12:09.290 --> 12:11.090
♪ Tomorrow seems so far away ♪

12:11.280 --> 12:12.760
♪ Everything is spinning ♪

12:12.910 --> 12:14.000
It's the second prize!

12:13.270 --> 12:15.760
♪ Do you want to hold me tight? ♪

12:14.510 --> 12:15.840
A motorcycle! Motorcycle!

12:15.840 --> 12:17.550
It seems another customer

12:16.300 --> 12:20.480
♪ Ho Yuet-tai, Chan Po-lai, Ng Yuen-tsai ♪

12:17.600 --> 12:18.510
has lucked out!

12:18.630 --> 12:20.630
Let's see which grand prize on stage

12:20.840 --> 12:22.550
he will

12:21.350 --> 12:22.940
♪ Ngai Shuk-fai, Szehung Man-wai ♪

12:22.600 --> 12:24.600
take home.

12:22.960 --> 12:27.190
♪ Snakes and ants, Lau Ping-tai,
and the Gods combined ♪

12:24.720 --> 12:26.630
This gentleman won the second prize.

12:26.630 --> 12:28.390
We've got the second winner

12:28.440 --> 12:29.600
of the second prize!

12:28.520 --> 12:33.190
♪ All of them start dancing, feet up,
legs turning and heads twisting ♪

12:29.840 --> 12:31.240
The prize is our motorcycle!

12:31.240 --> 12:32.630
Freshly made box lunches!

12:32.630 --> 12:33.910
Free rice refills.

12:33.570 --> 12:38.940
♪ Do you wanna dance tonight? ♪

12:33.960 --> 12:35.200
Free rice refills!

12:35.240 --> 12:36.170
Are you excited?

12:36.200 --> 12:36.790
Yes!

12:37.120 --> 12:37.920
Are you happy?

12:37.960 --> 12:38.510
Yes!

12:38.670 --> 12:39.630
Are you thrilled?

12:39.630 --> 12:40.200
Yes!

12:48.910 --> 12:50.000
1.86 million!

12:51.510 --> 12:52.360
Brat Ji,

12:53.080 --> 12:54.480
I'm going to win for sure.

12:54.910 --> 12:55.970
Congratulations.

12:56.150 --> 12:57.000
Same to you.

13:01.080 --> 13:01.880
What's wrong?

13:02.390 --> 13:04.190
Are you worried about Du Zhaoji?

13:04.360 --> 13:05.630
Tomorrow is the last day

13:05.630 --> 13:06.560
of the lucky draw

13:06.670 --> 13:09.000
as well as the last day
of the competition.

13:09.480 --> 13:10.390
It's been two days,

13:10.390 --> 13:11.920
and nothing has gone wrong.

13:12.360 --> 13:13.030
Besides,

13:13.360 --> 13:15.240
we've screened everyone.

13:15.960 --> 13:16.760
It'll be fine.

13:23.080 --> 13:23.880
Hello, Mr. Du.

13:23.920 --> 13:27.230
[Day 3 of the Electronics City's opening]

13:25.120 --> 13:25.670
Mr. Du,

13:25.720 --> 13:27.250
you really have foresight.

13:27.340 --> 13:28.440
This lucky draw event is

13:28.440 --> 13:29.320
a big hit!

13:29.440 --> 13:29.970
Look.

13:30.000 --> 13:31.600
My goods are almost sold out.

13:31.670 --> 13:32.960
Restock quickly
if you're running out of them.

13:32.960 --> 13:34.120
No problem.

13:34.120 --> 13:34.750
Mr. Du,

13:35.030 --> 13:36.480
please hold more events

13:36.550 --> 13:37.750
like this lucky draw.

13:37.910 --> 13:38.750
I will, definitely.

13:38.750 --> 13:40.350
Young Master! Young Master!

13:40.960 --> 13:43.160
S-Something really happened outside.

13:45.200 --> 13:47.080
Everyone, please judge this for me!

13:47.080 --> 13:48.240
This unscrupulous mall is

13:48.240 --> 13:50.080
selling shady electronics!

13:50.600 --> 13:52.030
Excuse us. Excuse us.

13:53.120 --> 13:54.720
Young Master! Young Master!

13:54.960 --> 13:55.720
Look!

13:55.870 --> 13:56.240
Young Master!

13:56.240 --> 13:57.500
We want to see the boss!

13:57.600 --> 13:59.270
We want an explanation!

14:01.200 --> 14:02.910
You're the boss
of this Electronics City, aren't you?

14:02.910 --> 14:04.200
I've seen you on TV.

14:04.360 --> 14:05.960
Look at the radio you sold us!

14:06.120 --> 14:08.080
It blew up my husband's hand!

14:08.520 --> 14:09.580
Our family depends on him

14:09.580 --> 14:10.820
to make money.

14:11.150 --> 14:12.670
Our child is so little.

14:13.150 --> 14:14.000
Tell me,

14:14.030 --> 14:15.440
what are we going to do?

14:19.870 --> 14:21.360
Give me an explanation now!

14:21.360 --> 14:22.960
Compensate me immediately!

14:23.510 --> 14:25.440
You need evidence for such claims.

14:26.480 --> 14:26.870
What?

14:27.240 --> 14:28.120
This radio already blew up

14:28.120 --> 14:29.100
my husband's hand.

14:29.100 --> 14:30.320
Are you going to hurt his other hand

14:30.320 --> 14:31.550
in front of the crowd?

14:31.870 --> 14:33.200
Is there no law anymore?

14:33.440 --> 14:35.270
Everyone, please help me judge this!

14:35.270 --> 14:35.930
Judge this!

14:36.000 --> 14:37.200
Everyone, calm down.

14:37.220 --> 14:37.960
Calm down, everyone.

14:37.960 --> 14:39.360
Listen to me. Hear me out.

14:39.390 --> 14:41.440
I am the boss of the Electronics City.

14:41.440 --> 14:41.750
Hua.

14:41.750 --> 14:42.640
Please calm down first.

14:42.640 --> 14:43.510
The police should be here soon.

14:43.510 --> 14:44.440
Go and meet them.

14:44.520 --> 14:45.390
If we really sold

14:45.390 --> 14:46.600
defective products,

14:46.960 --> 14:47.790
we'd definitely give everyone

14:47.790 --> 14:48.670
an explanation.

14:48.670 --> 14:50.150
What kind of quality product could it be?

14:50.150 --> 14:50.750
Would a quality product

14:50.750 --> 14:52.150
blow up my husband's hand like this?

14:52.150 --> 14:53.270
It blew up my hand like this!

14:53.270 --> 14:54.130
Check this out!

14:54.150 --> 14:55.080
Officers!

14:55.270 --> 14:55.960
Officers!

14:57.390 --> 14:58.240
Someone said

14:58.550 --> 14:59.560
that his hand was

14:59.750 --> 15:01.150
blown up, officers.

15:01.630 --> 15:03.670
How dare they sell fakes
right after opening?

15:03.670 --> 15:04.600
Excuse me! Excuse me!

15:04.600 --> 15:05.510
The police are here!

15:05.510 --> 15:06.640
The police are here!

15:07.000 --> 15:07.960
The police are here!

15:07.960 --> 15:08.560
Step back!

15:09.670 --> 15:10.750
Who's in charge here?

15:10.750 --> 15:12.000
Tell me what's going on.

15:12.000 --> 15:12.720
Officer,

15:12.750 --> 15:13.840
I'm the person in charge here.

15:13.840 --> 15:15.000
My name is Xia Xiaolan.

15:15.000 --> 15:15.860
Let me explain.

15:16.120 --> 15:16.960
Early this morning,

15:16.960 --> 15:18.130
before the Electronics City even opened,

15:18.130 --> 15:19.720
these two came here to make a scene,

15:19.720 --> 15:20.750
claiming that a radio

15:20.750 --> 15:22.480
exploded and injured his hand.

15:23.390 --> 15:25.000
Tomorrow is the last day of the lottery

15:25.000 --> 15:26.510
and also the last day of the competition.

15:26.510 --> 15:27.790
We won't need the scenarios

15:27.790 --> 15:29.390
we rehearsed before, right?

15:29.390 --> 15:31.150
We still can't let our guard down.

15:31.150 --> 15:32.950
We must be prepared at all times.

15:33.120 --> 15:34.360
But this is Shengcheng.

15:34.360 --> 15:35.980
Even if Du Zhaoji wants to cause trouble,

15:35.980 --> 15:36.910
he wouldn't dare to openly

15:36.910 --> 15:38.040
resort to violence.

15:38.200 --> 15:39.910
I guess the most likely scenario is

15:39.910 --> 15:40.670
that he'll make up

15:40.670 --> 15:42.120
a quality issue with the appliances

15:42.120 --> 15:43.850
to accuse you of selling fakes.

15:44.330 --> 15:45.670
If he's even more vicious,

15:45.670 --> 15:47.360
he might stage an injury incident

15:47.360 --> 15:49.290
caused by an appliance explosion.

15:49.550 --> 15:50.410
We're done for.

15:50.600 --> 15:51.480
That Brat Ji is

15:52.150 --> 15:53.750
definitely vicious enough.

15:54.030 --> 15:54.890
No matter what,

15:55.000 --> 15:55.980
just remember

15:56.200 --> 15:57.660
that you play the good cop,

15:57.720 --> 15:58.750
and I play the bad cop.

15:58.750 --> 16:00.670
Just don't get too into character,

16:00.670 --> 16:01.240
blurting out

16:01.240 --> 16:02.200
some profanity.

16:02.840 --> 16:03.600
I see.

16:03.870 --> 16:05.670
If someone comes to my turf
to cause trouble,

16:05.670 --> 16:07.120
I still have to play the nice guy?

16:07.120 --> 16:08.930
Just thinking about it makes me mad.

16:08.930 --> 16:10.600
Those people aren't your audience.

16:10.600 --> 16:12.130
You're acting for your dad.

16:12.630 --> 16:13.240
I know.

16:15.080 --> 16:16.030
Now I'm more worried

16:16.030 --> 16:17.490
about your acting skills.

16:18.080 --> 16:18.810
Don't worry.

16:19.000 --> 16:20.600
I've got the vibe team ready.

16:21.030 --> 16:22.320
You've done all the talking.

16:22.320 --> 16:22.840
As I see it,

16:22.840 --> 16:24.120
firstly, you have no proof of purchase.

16:24.120 --> 16:25.080
Secondly, you don't have

16:25.080 --> 16:26.840
that so-called exploded radio.

16:26.840 --> 16:27.390
Are you two

16:27.390 --> 16:28.600
here to scam us?

16:28.910 --> 16:30.040
You're the scammer!

16:30.120 --> 16:30.510
You are!

16:30.510 --> 16:31.200
-Xiaolan.
-I think you...

16:31.200 --> 16:32.030
Stop it for now.

16:32.030 --> 16:33.390
Since the officers are here,

16:33.390 --> 16:35.000
let them help us sort this out.

16:35.000 --> 16:35.600
Officers,

16:36.150 --> 16:36.780
I think

16:36.870 --> 16:37.790
we should send this gentleman

16:37.790 --> 16:38.670
to the hospital first.

16:38.670 --> 16:39.670
His hand is still bleeding.

16:39.670 --> 16:41.630
He probably just bandaged it himself.

16:41.630 --> 16:42.270
Yeah!

16:42.270 --> 16:43.670
His hand is still dripping blood!

16:43.670 --> 16:44.390
Go check it at the hospital.

16:44.390 --> 16:46.120
This boss looks like a nice guy.

16:46.240 --> 16:46.900
Okay, okay.

16:47.120 --> 16:47.600
Yeah, yeah.

16:47.600 --> 16:48.080
I only need compensation.

16:48.080 --> 16:49.270
I think I have a rough idea of it.

16:49.270 --> 16:50.000
We police

16:50.030 --> 16:51.000
won't let a big mall

16:51.000 --> 16:52.440
bully an ordinary citizen.

16:52.440 --> 16:53.390
Let's go to the hospital first

16:53.390 --> 16:54.750
and treat the wound on your hand.

16:54.750 --> 16:55.320
After that,

16:55.320 --> 16:56.790
we will investigate the situation

16:56.790 --> 16:58.120
and get justice for you.

16:58.150 --> 16:58.510
Okay?

16:58.790 --> 16:59.750
They haven't compensated us yet.

16:59.750 --> 17:00.910
Yes, please go to the hospital first.

17:00.910 --> 17:01.840
My colleague has already

17:01.840 --> 17:02.750
got the car ready.

17:02.750 --> 17:03.320
Go to the hospital!

17:03.320 --> 17:04.109
If anyone

17:04.349 --> 17:05.790
wants to be kept updated,

17:05.990 --> 17:07.030
you may as well come along.

17:07.030 --> 17:07.619
Is that okay?

17:07.619 --> 17:08.000
Officers,

17:08.000 --> 17:08.960
what do you think?

17:08.960 --> 17:10.240
-I'll go.
-Let's go.

17:10.270 --> 17:11.240
Go to the hospital now.

17:11.240 --> 17:11.720
Hurry up.

17:11.720 --> 17:13.119
Go get that hand checked.

17:13.920 --> 17:14.349
Hurry up and go.

17:14.349 --> 17:16.290
You might lose your hand
if you don't go quickly.

17:16.290 --> 17:18.010
Hurry up. Just go.

17:25.960 --> 17:27.220
Folks staying behind,

17:27.550 --> 17:28.270
our Electronics City is

17:28.270 --> 17:29.270
still open as usual.

17:29.270 --> 17:30.120
You can continue shopping.

17:30.120 --> 17:31.110
And our grand prize

17:31.110 --> 17:32.310
hasn't been drawn yet.

17:32.310 --> 17:32.790
Later,

17:32.790 --> 17:33.960
I will give everyone an explanation.

17:33.960 --> 17:34.310
Okay. Let's go.

17:34.310 --> 17:35.400
Come on, let's shop!

17:35.400 --> 17:36.830
Everyone, come in and shop.

17:36.830 --> 17:38.360
Come on, guys. Go shopping!

17:43.630 --> 17:46.150
[Emergency]

17:54.400 --> 17:55.640
This is a crush injury,

17:55.640 --> 17:56.550
not a blast one.

17:56.750 --> 17:58.160
C-crush injury. It's a crush injury.

17:58.160 --> 17:59.170
Can you tell

17:59.200 --> 18:00.200
what smashed it?

18:00.510 --> 18:02.110
A blast injury usually leaves burn marks.

18:02.110 --> 18:03.240
He doesn't have any.

18:03.310 --> 18:03.720
Look,

18:04.000 --> 18:05.330
his wound is irregular.

18:05.640 --> 18:07.160
And there's sand inside.

18:07.570 --> 18:08.400
Obviously, this was

18:08.400 --> 18:10.530
crushed by a heavy object like a stone.

18:10.550 --> 18:11.410
A crush injury?

18:11.750 --> 18:12.720
Then it's not a problem

18:12.720 --> 18:13.310
with the radio.

18:13.310 --> 18:13.720
Right.

18:13.830 --> 18:15.270
It has nothing to do with the mall.

18:15.270 --> 18:15.590
Right.

18:15.590 --> 18:16.550
-Exactly.
-Yeah.

18:16.550 --> 18:17.850
Yeah, officers.

18:18.160 --> 18:19.510
He got up early in the morning

18:19.510 --> 18:20.600
to cause trouble at the mall.

18:20.600 --> 18:22.240
He must've been there to extort money.

18:22.240 --> 18:23.130
-Right.
-Yeah.

18:23.160 --> 18:25.400
I think they must've come to scam people.

18:25.400 --> 18:27.310
They brought such a small child out.

18:27.310 --> 18:29.000
Is it even their own child?

18:29.020 --> 18:30.030
You've got a point.

18:30.030 --> 18:31.830
Could they be human traffickers?

18:31.830 --> 18:32.270
Right!

18:32.310 --> 18:33.110
Are they human traffickers?

18:33.110 --> 18:34.370
Everyone, quiet down.

18:34.590 --> 18:35.720
You two, come clean.

18:35.830 --> 18:36.960
This is clearly a crush injury.

18:36.960 --> 18:37.550
Why did you say it was

18:37.550 --> 18:38.920
from the radio explosion?

18:38.920 --> 18:39.680
Officers...

18:39.790 --> 18:41.200
Officers protect good people

18:41.200 --> 18:42.130
and fight crime.

18:42.440 --> 18:42.960
Our mall is

18:42.960 --> 18:44.350
the biggest victim, actually.

18:44.350 --> 18:45.680
Explain it clearly to them.

18:45.680 --> 18:47.550
Luckily, we live in a society of laws.

18:47.550 --> 18:48.590
In the old days,

18:48.680 --> 18:49.750
scammers like you

18:49.880 --> 18:50.640
would get beaten up

18:50.640 --> 18:51.290
and thrown out.

18:51.290 --> 18:51.830
Right.

18:51.850 --> 18:53.160
People with such black hearts

18:53.160 --> 18:54.110
should be beaten up.

18:54.110 --> 18:54.970
Yeah, beat him!

18:56.750 --> 18:58.030
Quiet, everyone. Quiet.

18:58.030 --> 18:58.690
Fine, fine.

18:58.830 --> 18:59.630
I'll confess.

19:00.070 --> 19:00.790
My husband's hand wasn't

19:00.790 --> 19:02.030
blown up by the radio.

19:02.480 --> 19:03.440
Someone paid us

19:03.510 --> 19:05.270
to cause trouble at the Electronics City.

19:05.270 --> 19:07.110
They said I could keep the compensation

19:07.110 --> 19:09.000
from the Electronics City for myself.

19:09.000 --> 19:09.880
Officers,

19:10.000 --> 19:11.350
I had no choice.

19:11.550 --> 19:12.440
My husband's hand was

19:12.440 --> 19:14.110
crushed at the construction site.

19:14.110 --> 19:15.970
We haven't had any income lately.

19:16.030 --> 19:17.650
The child is sick,

19:18.070 --> 19:19.870
and we need money for the doctor.

19:20.350 --> 19:21.640
Stop playing the victim.

19:21.640 --> 19:22.960
It wasn't the Electronics City

19:22.960 --> 19:23.590
that hurt him.

19:23.590 --> 19:24.000
Exactly.

19:24.000 --> 19:25.480
Settle the score with the one responsible.

19:25.480 --> 19:26.680
If everyone acted like you,

19:26.680 --> 19:28.110
how could they do business?

19:28.110 --> 19:29.840
-Exactly!
-Indeed!

19:29.870 --> 19:30.870
Quiet, everyone.

19:30.920 --> 19:32.240
Mr. Du happens to be here, too.

19:32.240 --> 19:33.400
Let's listen to his opinion

19:33.400 --> 19:35.200
and see how he wants to handle this.

19:35.200 --> 19:35.640
Mr. Du,

19:36.160 --> 19:37.640
even if you dock my pay today,

19:37.640 --> 19:38.590
I still have to say this.

19:38.590 --> 19:39.400
They must've been sent

19:39.400 --> 19:40.090
by our competitor

19:40.090 --> 19:41.240
to cause trouble on purpose.

19:41.240 --> 19:42.000
That's right.

19:42.000 --> 19:43.510
Mr. Du, you're normally too kind.

19:43.510 --> 19:44.440
You can't be like that anymore...

19:44.440 --> 19:45.440
Since it's a scam,

19:45.790 --> 19:47.310
let's leave it for the officers to handle.

19:47.310 --> 19:48.910
But let me add one more thing.

19:49.070 --> 19:50.880
You should take the child to see a doctor.

19:50.880 --> 19:52.720
I've watched him cry this whole time.

19:52.720 --> 19:53.880
I find your slander

19:53.930 --> 19:55.260
against us despicable,

19:55.560 --> 19:56.150
but

19:56.690 --> 19:57.450
the police

19:57.480 --> 19:58.880
will help me settle this.

19:59.410 --> 20:00.880
No matter what bad intentions
the bad guys harbour,

20:00.880 --> 20:02.140
the child is innocent.

20:02.200 --> 20:03.400
Get him treated first.

20:03.400 --> 20:05.000
I'll pay your medical bills.

20:05.590 --> 20:07.000
Thank you, sir. Thank you.

20:07.000 --> 20:08.160
You guys are so lucky

20:08.160 --> 20:09.370
that you ran into such a nice boss!

20:09.370 --> 20:10.400
He's so benevolent, right?

20:10.400 --> 20:11.440
Yeah, so benevolent!

20:11.440 --> 20:12.550
It's such a poor child,

20:12.550 --> 20:13.270
suffering a lot.

20:13.270 --> 20:14.930
What kind of parents are they?

20:15.750 --> 20:17.550
They used a child to make a scene!

20:24.960 --> 20:25.350
Bro,

20:25.960 --> 20:27.160
where is that couple?

20:27.270 --> 20:27.870
Forget it.

20:28.070 --> 20:29.200
Come on! Raise the banners!

20:29.200 --> 20:29.860
Raise them.

20:29.920 --> 20:30.350
Hurry!

20:30.450 --> 20:31.570
[The shady Electronics City
sold fakes and hurt people!]

20:31.400 --> 20:32.530
Come and take a look!

20:32.830 --> 20:35.030
The shady Electronics City sold fakes!

20:35.350 --> 20:37.150
They sold fakes and hurt people!

20:37.480 --> 20:37.960
What?

20:38.160 --> 20:38.840
What are you doing?

20:38.840 --> 20:39.680
What are you doing?

20:39.680 --> 20:40.070
What do you want?

20:40.070 --> 20:41.000
Go back. Go back.

20:41.440 --> 20:42.300
Don't touch me.

20:42.590 --> 20:43.030
What?

20:43.400 --> 20:44.200
Without the troublemakers,

20:44.200 --> 20:45.110
you don't know how to put on the show,

20:45.110 --> 20:45.550
right?

20:46.540 --> 20:48.070
Let's go. I'll take you there.

20:48.070 --> 20:48.510
Take them away.

20:48.510 --> 20:48.880
Move!

20:48.960 --> 20:50.480
-Go!
-Hands off! Don't push!

20:50.480 --> 20:51.160
Don't push!

20:51.310 --> 20:52.130
They'll surely not only

20:52.130 --> 20:53.200
stir up public opinion

20:53.200 --> 20:54.860
but also prepare a follow-up.

20:56.680 --> 20:57.920
The troublemakers are the vanguard.

20:57.920 --> 20:59.590
The others are rooting for them.

20:59.590 --> 21:01.450
That's how the topic stays alive.

21:02.350 --> 21:03.440
If Du Zhaoji

21:03.440 --> 21:03.880
really plays

21:03.880 --> 21:05.070
such dirty tricks,

21:05.400 --> 21:06.030
we must

21:06.030 --> 21:07.110
shift the scene of the incident

21:07.110 --> 21:08.200
to somewhere else

21:08.590 --> 21:09.440
and not let people

21:09.440 --> 21:11.000
gather at the entrance
of the Electronics City.

21:11.000 --> 21:12.400
Otherwise, rumors will spread,

21:12.400 --> 21:13.510
and we can't explain it, no matter what.

21:13.510 --> 21:14.750
Go, go!

21:14.750 --> 21:15.790
Move! Quickly!

21:17.640 --> 21:18.900
I drew the first prize!

21:19.070 --> 21:20.270
I won the first prize!

21:21.360 --> 21:22.070
The first prize!

21:22.070 --> 21:23.400
The first prize! First prize!

21:23.400 --> 21:24.600
I won the first prize!

21:24.610 --> 21:25.540
The first prize!

21:26.750 --> 21:27.950
I got the first prize!

21:28.830 --> 21:30.430
I'm the first-prize winner!

21:36.240 --> 21:37.160
First prize! I got the first prize!

21:37.160 --> 21:38.350
Chengrong Electronics City

21:38.350 --> 21:39.510
has been open for 3 days,

21:39.510 --> 21:40.240
and we've finally got

21:40.240 --> 21:41.330
the first-prize winner!

21:41.330 --> 21:42.290
Let's give a round of applause

21:42.290 --> 21:44.150
to congratulate this gentleman!

21:46.550 --> 21:47.030
I...

21:47.310 --> 21:48.550
I'm really not a shill!

21:48.550 --> 21:50.080
I'm a bit excited right now.

21:50.510 --> 21:51.950
I just bought a radio.

21:52.110 --> 21:53.720
I spent around 100 yuan.

21:53.760 --> 21:55.130
T-This car...

21:55.240 --> 21:56.040
It's mine now!

21:56.960 --> 21:57.510
Bravo!

22:00.510 --> 22:01.200
Thank you!

22:01.270 --> 22:02.980
Thank you, Chengrong Electronics City!

22:02.980 --> 22:05.030
Such an organized and premeditated act was

22:05.030 --> 22:06.200
probably not just

22:06.200 --> 22:07.440
business competition.

22:07.440 --> 22:08.440
I suspect someone

22:08.510 --> 22:09.310
wanted to create

22:09.310 --> 22:11.030
a mass panic incident on purpose.

22:11.030 --> 22:11.550
Yes.

22:11.960 --> 22:13.960
Luckily, the police arrived in time.

22:13.960 --> 22:15.350
And these enthusiastic customers

22:15.350 --> 22:16.830
came up with solutions for me.

22:16.830 --> 22:18.070
Otherwise, it would've turned into rumors

22:18.070 --> 22:20.750
about the Electronics City
selling fake or inferior products

22:20.750 --> 22:21.920
and causing injuries to customers

22:21.920 --> 22:22.720
for sure.

22:23.440 --> 22:24.640
Since you saw everything

22:24.640 --> 22:25.720
from beginning to end today,

22:25.720 --> 22:26.400
if you hear

22:26.400 --> 22:27.590
any rumors in the future,

22:27.590 --> 22:29.200
please defend me.

22:29.440 --> 22:29.880
Thank you.

22:29.880 --> 22:30.590
That's for sure.

22:30.590 --> 22:31.720
We'll definitely explain it clearly.

22:31.720 --> 22:32.450
Don't worry.

22:32.510 --> 22:32.880
Yeah.

22:32.880 --> 22:33.640
Mr. Du, rest assured.

22:33.640 --> 22:34.920
So many of us saw it.

22:35.110 --> 22:36.310
If anyone spreads rumors,

22:36.310 --> 22:37.310
we'll defend you.

22:37.510 --> 22:39.110
The police will also arrest them.

22:39.110 --> 22:39.790
Thank you. Many thanks.

22:39.790 --> 22:40.240
Right, right.

22:40.240 --> 22:40.960
Officers,

22:41.030 --> 22:42.240
please find those behind this
and bring them

22:42.240 --> 22:42.880
to justice.

22:42.880 --> 22:43.640
Yes.

22:43.680 --> 22:44.350
Come in, come in.

22:44.350 --> 22:45.310
Hurry.

22:46.920 --> 22:47.510
You guys,

22:48.480 --> 22:49.340
go to that room.

22:57.030 --> 22:57.760
How did it go?

22:57.880 --> 22:58.340
Ms. Xia,

22:58.550 --> 22:59.680
we caught a few agitators

22:59.680 --> 23:00.880
at the mall entrance.

23:00.920 --> 23:01.880
They didn't even know

23:01.880 --> 23:02.480
what had happened,

23:02.480 --> 23:03.880
yet they still came with banners,

23:03.880 --> 23:04.880
claiming that the Electronics City

23:04.880 --> 23:06.680
sold products that hurt people.

23:06.830 --> 23:07.310
Thankfully,

23:07.310 --> 23:08.440
a few plainclothes police were

23:08.440 --> 23:09.480
patrolling nearby.

23:09.480 --> 23:11.010
They found them suspicious

23:11.110 --> 23:11.880
and helped us

23:12.070 --> 23:12.960
subdue them.

23:15.350 --> 23:15.920
Officer,

23:16.270 --> 23:17.750
you must investigate this thoroughly.

23:17.750 --> 23:18.590
The Electronics City's business

23:18.590 --> 23:19.550
taking a hit is nothing.

23:19.550 --> 23:21.350
Everyone's safety comes first.

23:21.480 --> 23:23.030
If we don't find the mastermind,

23:23.030 --> 23:24.160
I won't feel at ease.

23:24.270 --> 23:24.720
Yes!

23:24.750 --> 23:25.830
Investigate thoroughly!

23:25.830 --> 23:27.070
Don't let them go until it's clear.

23:27.070 --> 23:27.930
Yes! That's it!

23:28.000 --> 23:29.200
And the woman who looks after the child

23:29.200 --> 23:30.130
in the hospital,

23:30.200 --> 23:30.960
she definitely knows.

23:30.960 --> 23:31.360
Right.

23:31.480 --> 23:32.810
Yes, yes. She must know.

23:33.510 --> 23:34.640
Quiet down, everyone.

23:34.640 --> 23:35.880
We will definitely get to the bottom of it

23:35.880 --> 23:37.590
and give everyone a satisfactory answer.

23:37.590 --> 23:38.850
Please go back for now.

23:40.000 --> 23:40.650
You two,

23:40.920 --> 23:42.510
come with me to give a statement.

23:42.510 --> 23:42.880
Okay.

23:44.030 --> 23:44.630
I'm going.

23:46.200 --> 23:46.800
Thank you.

23:46.830 --> 23:47.430
Thank you.

23:48.030 --> 23:49.630
Thank you. Thank you so much.

23:57.200 --> 23:57.750
Mr. Du,

23:58.440 --> 24:00.310
how does it feel to be a good guy?

24:00.960 --> 24:01.840
You know what?

24:02.000 --> 24:03.270
When people call me a nice guy,

24:03.270 --> 24:04.920
I actually feel a bit carried away.

24:04.920 --> 24:06.650
Have you enjoyed acting today?

24:07.110 --> 24:08.570
It's just part of the plot.

24:09.730 --> 24:10.750
Although this matter is

24:10.750 --> 24:12.010
considered resolved,

24:12.120 --> 24:13.040
our business

24:13.070 --> 24:15.130
has still been affected, obviously.

24:15.160 --> 24:16.000
The foot traffic is

24:16.000 --> 24:17.830
much less than it was 2 days ago.

24:18.590 --> 24:19.590
Tomorrow I have to report accounts

24:19.590 --> 24:20.390
to the Old Man.

24:20.720 --> 24:22.050
I think I'll be done for.

24:22.720 --> 24:24.170
I underestimated the enemy.

24:24.170 --> 24:25.450
Brat Ji is

24:25.480 --> 24:26.350
literally a wolf

24:26.350 --> 24:27.480
in sheep's clothing.

24:27.480 --> 24:28.210
I should have

24:28.240 --> 24:30.040
taken the initiative to strike.

24:30.110 --> 24:32.170
Chairman Du is a shrewd businessman.

24:32.310 --> 24:33.640
If he really only looked

24:33.790 --> 24:35.200
at the sales figures before the deadline

24:35.200 --> 24:36.160
of the competition,

24:36.160 --> 24:38.420
your chances weren't high to begin with.

24:39.240 --> 24:40.770
I think this competition is

24:40.960 --> 24:42.720
also about investment vision

24:42.750 --> 24:44.350
and long-term development.

24:44.750 --> 24:46.960
The Electronics City
has a long future ahead.

24:46.960 --> 24:48.160
I believe Chairman Du

24:48.160 --> 24:49.510
would also want the Chengrong Group

24:49.510 --> 24:50.970
to prosper for a long time.

24:51.240 --> 24:52.040
It is still

24:52.070 --> 24:52.930
anyone's game.

24:53.750 --> 24:54.880
Stop comforting me.

24:54.960 --> 24:55.890
You guys go back first.

24:55.890 --> 24:57.420
I want to cry alone for a bit.

24:57.640 --> 24:59.240
Young Master! Young Master!

24:59.480 --> 25:00.440
About the invitation

25:00.440 --> 25:02.160
to the Master's birthday banquet,

25:02.160 --> 25:02.510
I haven't...

25:02.510 --> 25:04.160
Don't be silly. What invitation?

25:04.160 --> 25:04.830
Can I not go?

25:05.550 --> 25:06.480
It's not for you.

25:06.830 --> 25:07.400
Ms. Xia.

25:10.110 --> 25:11.640
The Master sent this to you.

25:15.000 --> 25:16.660
Alright, we're leaving then.

25:17.400 --> 25:18.480
-Bye-bye, Bye-bye.
-Bye-bye.

25:18.480 --> 25:19.010
Goodbye.

25:21.590 --> 25:22.590
Why give it to her?

25:22.960 --> 25:24.360
You may go ask the Master.

25:29.510 --> 25:30.790
The Chengrong Group has long

25:30.790 --> 25:32.720
wanted to build a factory in the mainland.

25:32.720 --> 25:33.550
But we suspect

25:33.550 --> 25:34.790
the source of their funds,

25:34.790 --> 25:36.250
so we haven't approved it.

25:36.880 --> 25:38.600
He told you about the smuggling

25:38.600 --> 25:39.860
to curry favor with me.

25:40.590 --> 25:42.550
Inviting you to the birthday banquet is

25:42.550 --> 25:44.080
also a gesture of goodwill.

25:45.000 --> 25:46.030
But don't worry.

25:46.440 --> 25:47.170
The Du family

25:47.440 --> 25:49.300
wouldn't dare do anything to you.

25:49.920 --> 25:50.550
Xiaolan,

25:51.160 --> 25:52.290
you must be careful.

25:58.640 --> 26:01.200
[General Manager's Office]

25:59.110 --> 25:59.570
Come in.

26:03.850 --> 26:04.780
[Resignation]

26:05.510 --> 26:06.110
Ms. Xia,

26:06.960 --> 26:08.890
I have to confess something to you.

26:09.310 --> 26:10.920
Your past grudges against Nie Weiguo

26:10.920 --> 26:12.270
in Jiangcheng

26:12.680 --> 26:13.640
might be because of me...

26:13.640 --> 26:14.970
I knew all that already.

26:16.280 --> 26:17.480
Then why did you still let me help

26:17.480 --> 26:19.280
prepare the lawsuit materials?

26:20.830 --> 26:22.160
Because I don't believe

26:22.180 --> 26:24.180
you would betray Qi Hang on purpose.

26:25.310 --> 26:27.040
Perhaps it was unintentional.

26:27.270 --> 26:28.070
But I didn't want

26:28.070 --> 26:29.470
to label you as a traitor.

26:29.480 --> 26:30.240
I also wanted to see

26:30.240 --> 26:32.040
how you'd handle it afterwards.

26:33.200 --> 26:34.260
Ms. Xia, I'm sorry.

26:35.400 --> 26:36.700
Someone contacted me before, saying they

26:36.700 --> 26:37.920
wanted to buy my oil paintings,

26:37.920 --> 26:40.180
and they had a way
to sell them to Gangdao.

26:40.440 --> 26:41.240
My artistic ideal

26:41.240 --> 26:42.590
kicked in again.

26:43.110 --> 26:44.880
I didn't pay much attention
while chatting.

26:44.880 --> 26:45.750
He'd occasionally ask me

26:45.750 --> 26:46.950
about my recent work.

26:47.030 --> 26:48.560
I talked about it casually.

26:48.750 --> 26:49.610
I didn't expect

26:49.720 --> 26:51.450
it would cause so much trouble.

26:51.480 --> 26:53.140
I shouldn't have said so much.

26:55.640 --> 26:56.880
You tried to make amends

26:56.880 --> 26:58.830
and were brave to take responsibility.

26:58.830 --> 27:00.430
I knew I didn't misjudge you.

27:01.400 --> 27:02.000
But this is

27:02.640 --> 27:04.440
not the best solution right now.

27:04.880 --> 27:05.740
Whether for you

27:05.830 --> 27:07.240
or for Qi Hang,

27:07.310 --> 27:08.310
it would be a loss.

27:09.920 --> 27:10.520
Gong Yang,

27:11.070 --> 27:12.750
take this resignation back for now.

27:12.750 --> 27:14.310
I'm going to Gangdao in a few days.

27:14.310 --> 27:15.000
When I get back,

27:15.000 --> 27:16.460
I'll tell you my decision.

27:21.240 --> 27:22.700
-Xiaolan.
-What's wrong?

27:22.880 --> 27:24.270
I'll go to Gangdao with you.

27:24.270 --> 27:25.000
San just contacted me,

27:25.000 --> 27:26.660
saying he got a new discovery.

27:27.510 --> 27:29.110
San is still investigating?

27:29.790 --> 27:30.270
Yes.

27:30.680 --> 27:32.280
I didn't expect that either.

27:33.910 --> 27:37.430
[Gangdao]

27:39.590 --> 27:40.390
Young Master,

27:40.450 --> 27:41.480
the Master and the Second Young Master are

27:41.480 --> 27:43.680
already waiting for you at the company.

27:47.160 --> 27:48.150
Rest assured, Young Master.

27:48.150 --> 27:49.350
We've also had someone

27:49.350 --> 27:50.720
protect Ms. Xia and Attorney Zhou.

27:50.720 --> 27:51.550
We will take them directly

27:51.550 --> 27:52.750
to the banquet venue.

27:53.790 --> 27:54.400
I see.

28:08.880 --> 28:09.960
Du Chengrong is

28:10.270 --> 28:11.800
quite a formidable figure.

28:12.070 --> 28:13.590
He went from a small-time thug

28:13.590 --> 28:15.990
to the big boss
of the mega Chengrong Group.

28:16.400 --> 28:16.960
I wonder how he

28:16.960 --> 28:18.400
made his fortune back then.

28:18.400 --> 28:20.200
It certainly wasn't clean.

28:21.510 --> 28:22.640
Do you think

28:23.550 --> 28:24.610
Du Zhaohui can win?

28:25.030 --> 28:26.480
No matter the result,

28:26.830 --> 28:27.880
the real winner

28:28.200 --> 28:29.720
can only be Chairman Du.

28:31.270 --> 28:32.350
He's already 60.

28:32.750 --> 28:33.810
The shares he holds

28:33.830 --> 28:36.110
will eventually be handed down
to his children.

28:36.110 --> 28:37.920
His two sons are both so outstanding.

28:37.920 --> 28:39.380
He has worthy successors.

28:40.720 --> 28:41.320
Isn't that

28:41.510 --> 28:43.240
what makes him the real winner?

28:43.790 --> 28:44.480
Sir,

28:44.720 --> 28:45.640
the number you just paged

28:45.640 --> 28:46.570
has called back.

28:46.960 --> 28:47.310
Okay.

28:52.480 --> 28:52.880
Hello?

28:57.480 --> 28:58.310
Okay, I got it.

28:59.270 --> 29:00.400
I'll be right there.

29:08.880 --> 29:10.140
Go ahead, don't worry.

29:10.270 --> 29:12.000
As long as I stay at the banquet,

29:12.070 --> 29:13.530
no one will cause trouble.

29:14.480 --> 29:15.110
Xia Ziyu will

29:15.110 --> 29:16.570
definitely attend today.

29:17.160 --> 29:17.830
Be careful.

29:18.480 --> 29:19.210
Don't worry.

29:19.790 --> 29:21.030
She has places to be.

29:21.350 --> 29:23.210
I won't cause trouble for myself.

29:27.000 --> 29:27.480
I'm off.

29:27.790 --> 29:28.440
Take care.

29:37.270 --> 29:38.730
Big Brother, you're here.

29:38.920 --> 29:40.550
Here's the financial report
for the Electronics City.

29:40.550 --> 29:42.310
According to the competition cycle,

29:42.310 --> 29:44.310
the data's updated up to yesterday.

29:48.440 --> 29:51.040
Yesterday's numbers dropped significantly.

29:51.440 --> 29:52.160
Dad,

29:52.640 --> 29:53.880
there are only the three of us Dus

29:53.880 --> 29:54.550
here.

29:54.920 --> 29:55.680
You don't have to pretend

29:55.680 --> 29:57.440
you don't know anything, right?

29:57.440 --> 29:59.690
Although I don't have any solid evidence,

29:59.690 --> 30:01.220
don't we all know who played

30:01.240 --> 30:01.970
dirty tricks

30:02.820 --> 30:03.670
behind this?

30:06.310 --> 30:08.310
Big Brother, are you suspecting me?

30:09.200 --> 30:11.130
I really can't prove my innocence.

30:11.310 --> 30:12.000
Zhaohui,

30:12.640 --> 30:13.920
based on the data,

30:14.270 --> 30:16.130
you indeed did worse than Zhaoji.

30:17.000 --> 30:18.270
Don't be so rigid.

30:18.680 --> 30:20.730
You're just looking at the profits
from these few days.

30:20.730 --> 30:21.680
Shouldn't you look at which project

30:21.680 --> 30:22.810
has more potential?

30:22.920 --> 30:23.590
And which project

30:23.590 --> 30:24.720
has more influence?

30:25.640 --> 30:27.110
In this competition, from start to finish,

30:27.110 --> 30:28.750
who actually played

30:28.750 --> 30:30.050
by the rules?

30:30.270 --> 30:31.530
Of our two industries,

30:31.680 --> 30:33.030
which one could be leveraged

30:33.030 --> 30:34.230
with just 20 million?

30:34.750 --> 30:37.240
I used 20 million
to build an Electronics City.

30:37.240 --> 30:38.440
Just one of Zhaoji's production lines

30:38.440 --> 30:40.440
in Thailand has cost more than that.

30:41.200 --> 30:41.680
Dad,

30:42.240 --> 30:43.000
if you're not interested

30:43.000 --> 30:44.030
in the Electronics City,

30:44.030 --> 30:45.960
I can take it back and run it myself.

30:46.030 --> 30:47.400
It won't get mixed up

30:47.400 --> 30:48.930
with the Group's business.

30:51.350 --> 30:51.790
Daddy!

30:52.720 --> 30:53.650
Don't get angry.

30:54.160 --> 30:55.090
I'm not dead yet!

30:55.310 --> 30:56.910
You want to split the family?

31:00.310 --> 31:01.170
Get out for now.

31:02.160 --> 31:03.020
I will announce

31:03.350 --> 31:05.950
the competition results later
at the banquet.

31:16.830 --> 31:18.560
Please feel free to contact me.

31:24.510 --> 31:25.710
Where is that Jerk...

31:25.930 --> 31:26.930
Where's Mr. Zhou?

31:27.380 --> 31:28.310
He has other business.

31:28.310 --> 31:30.440
He'll come pick me up when this is over.

31:31.600 --> 31:32.590
Your family's birthday banquet is

31:32.590 --> 31:33.790
quite the spectacle.

31:34.210 --> 31:35.000
It's alright.

31:35.000 --> 31:35.750
Just normal.

31:36.310 --> 31:36.770
Come on.

31:36.980 --> 31:38.180
Let me introduce you.

31:38.550 --> 31:40.060
Those at the tables in the back are

31:40.060 --> 31:40.860
all small fry.

31:40.960 --> 31:43.170
The important ones are
at the three in front.

31:43.170 --> 31:43.830
That table there is

31:43.830 --> 31:45.110
for my family members.

31:45.400 --> 31:46.200
Liu Tianquan.

31:46.230 --> 31:47.290
Next to him is his younger sister,

31:47.290 --> 31:48.020
Liu Keying.

31:48.160 --> 31:49.160
Before Vivi came,

31:49.270 --> 31:50.470
she was the favorite.

31:50.590 --> 31:51.640
Other women wouldn't even be

31:51.640 --> 31:52.840
qualified to be here.

31:53.390 --> 31:54.400
The table on the far right is

31:54.400 --> 31:55.460
also for insiders.

31:56.440 --> 31:58.040
What about the middle table?

31:59.110 --> 31:59.830
This table?

31:59.960 --> 32:01.030
It's really special.

32:01.030 --> 32:02.600
It's for veteran directors,

32:02.600 --> 32:03.340
those from the newspaper biz,

32:03.340 --> 32:04.590
and those from investment companies.

32:04.590 --> 32:05.680
They are all VIPs

32:05.680 --> 32:07.310
specially invited by the Old Man.

32:07.310 --> 32:08.710
The Old Man has a rule

32:09.200 --> 32:12.060
that our family members
can't sit at the main table.

32:13.390 --> 32:13.960
Mr. Meng.

32:14.200 --> 32:14.730
Zhaohui.

32:15.780 --> 32:16.570
This time,

32:16.790 --> 32:18.720
you really stole the show.

32:19.050 --> 32:19.980
You made it so big

32:20.070 --> 32:21.100
in Shengcheng

32:21.480 --> 32:23.350
that even I heard about it in Gangdao.

32:23.350 --> 32:24.640
Just a small business.

32:25.350 --> 32:26.680
I'll still need your support

32:26.680 --> 32:28.210
and guidance in the future.

32:30.920 --> 32:31.960
Is this your girlfriend?

32:31.960 --> 32:33.020
She's very pretty.

32:33.920 --> 32:35.480
Of course not, Mr. Meng.

32:36.110 --> 32:37.030
Ms. Xia is

32:37.030 --> 32:37.790
the Old Man's

32:37.790 --> 32:39.120
specially invited VIP.

32:39.240 --> 32:39.790
I'm not

32:40.030 --> 32:41.480
qualified to invite her.

32:42.750 --> 32:43.440
Ms. Xia,

32:43.640 --> 32:45.160
Chairman Du instructed us

32:45.160 --> 32:46.310
to prepare a seat for you.

32:46.310 --> 32:47.310
Please follow me.

32:47.850 --> 32:49.180
I'll take my leave then.

32:52.160 --> 32:53.200
No way.

32:54.070 --> 32:55.410
That's the VIP section.

32:55.720 --> 32:57.720
Did your dad invite her personally?

32:58.310 --> 32:59.200
I told you.

32:59.350 --> 33:00.310
She's a boss.

33:00.720 --> 33:02.180
Don't underestimate her.

33:02.270 --> 33:03.270
That impressive?

33:04.730 --> 33:06.000
Come on, take a seat first.

33:06.000 --> 33:06.960
After you, Mr. Meng.

33:06.960 --> 33:07.510
Okay.

33:09.750 --> 33:10.640
Hello, hello.

33:10.640 --> 33:11.240
Tianquan.

33:11.440 --> 33:11.960
Hello.

33:13.110 --> 33:13.710
Tianquan!

33:14.400 --> 33:15.070
How can you still

33:15.070 --> 33:16.680
be in the mood to look at women?

33:16.680 --> 33:18.270
Who exactly is that woman?

33:18.510 --> 33:20.160
How could she sit at that table?

33:20.160 --> 33:21.830
Don't underestimate her.

33:22.070 --> 33:23.590
She is the stepdaughter of Tang Hong'en,

33:23.590 --> 33:24.990
the Mayor of Shengcheng.

33:25.110 --> 33:26.480
It was just because of her

33:26.480 --> 33:27.790
that I couldn't expand my business

33:27.790 --> 33:29.110
in Shengcheng.

33:30.460 --> 33:31.370
Du Zhaohui

33:31.400 --> 33:33.030
only got to have smooth sailing

33:33.030 --> 33:35.270
because he rode on her coattails.

33:37.720 --> 33:38.790
Is that young woman

33:38.790 --> 33:40.110
so capable?

33:42.030 --> 33:44.690
No wonder Du Zhaohui
clings to her like a lapdog.

33:47.310 --> 33:48.370
You can't eat that.

33:48.750 --> 33:49.810
It'll make you fat,

33:49.830 --> 33:50.520
you know?

33:50.830 --> 33:51.240
Mommy.

33:51.750 --> 33:52.310
There you are.

33:52.310 --> 33:53.070
Sit down now.

33:55.880 --> 33:57.480
Did you see your big brother?

33:58.240 --> 34:00.640
Look at him.
He loves the spotlight so much.

34:01.640 --> 34:02.510
But your dad

34:02.510 --> 34:03.640
hates that the most.

34:04.160 --> 34:05.310
No manners.

34:05.510 --> 34:06.680
It's annoying.

34:07.160 --> 34:08.190
You must keep that in mind,

34:08.190 --> 34:08.920
understand?

34:09.630 --> 34:11.480
Big Brother is on good terms with Ms. Xia,

34:11.480 --> 34:13.480
so it's right for him to take care of her.

34:13.480 --> 34:14.280
What good terms?

34:14.280 --> 34:15.280
What friendship?

34:15.630 --> 34:17.320
I saw through him long ago.

34:17.590 --> 34:19.510
He goes wherever the money is.

34:19.920 --> 34:22.230
I have sharp eyes.

34:22.510 --> 34:23.570
Can't you see that?

34:24.800 --> 34:26.130
Here, drink some water.

34:26.480 --> 34:28.610
So, the project of Golden Sands Pool is

34:28.670 --> 34:29.670
your work?

34:29.880 --> 34:30.280
Yes.

34:30.510 --> 34:31.110
It's hers.

34:32.070 --> 34:34.190
Many people in Gangdao

34:34.360 --> 34:35.889
like this development.

34:36.400 --> 34:37.440
When will it go on sale?

34:37.440 --> 34:39.230
It's scheduled for this December.

34:39.230 --> 34:40.150
If I have time,

34:40.150 --> 34:41.000
I'll go take a look then.

34:41.000 --> 34:41.630
No problem.

34:41.630 --> 34:42.830
Everyone is welcome.

34:43.030 --> 34:43.670
For sure.

34:44.320 --> 34:46.360
At first, I didn't see it in you.

34:46.800 --> 34:48.800
You are truly young and successful.

34:51.710 --> 34:52.510
Mr. Du is here.

34:52.760 --> 34:53.550
Mr. Du!

35:29.510 --> 35:30.360
Thank you, everyone.

35:30.360 --> 35:31.110
Please sit down first.

35:31.110 --> 35:32.110
Please be seated.

35:32.800 --> 35:33.760
I'm going back to my seat.

35:33.760 --> 35:35.360
Mr. Meng, you're here!

35:37.840 --> 35:38.760
I'm so happy.

35:42.880 --> 35:43.450
Ms. Xia,

35:43.960 --> 35:45.820
I work in the newspaper industry.

35:45.880 --> 35:47.550
If you come to Gangdao
again in the future,

35:47.550 --> 35:48.480
feel free to contact me anytime.

35:48.480 --> 35:48.840
Okay.

35:50.230 --> 35:51.110
Stop looking.

35:51.760 --> 35:53.030
The Old Man has a rule.

35:53.280 --> 35:54.190
Family members are

35:54.190 --> 35:56.190
not allowed to sit at the main table.

35:59.510 --> 36:00.030
Let's

36:00.030 --> 36:01.360
keep in touch in the future.

36:01.360 --> 36:02.190
It would be my honor.

36:02.190 --> 36:04.440
I heard the Young Master
brought a female companion.

36:04.440 --> 36:05.030
Why didn't he

36:05.030 --> 36:06.360
introduce her to us all?

36:10.110 --> 36:10.710
Hello,

36:11.840 --> 36:12.510
Ms. Xia.

36:20.760 --> 36:21.710
Hello, Vivi.

36:24.110 --> 36:25.880
Since you're the Young Master's friend,

36:25.880 --> 36:27.480
you're a guest of our family.

36:27.710 --> 36:29.510
I'd like to propose a toast to you

36:29.930 --> 36:31.460
on behalf of Mr. Du, Ms. Xia.

36:39.230 --> 36:40.310
Not bad, Vivi.

36:41.360 --> 36:43.960
You're helping me
entertain my special guest.

36:44.360 --> 36:46.520
Ms. Xia is someone

36:46.760 --> 36:48.320
I specially invited here.

36:49.590 --> 36:50.450
How about this?

36:50.590 --> 36:52.150
You go back and sit down for a moment.

36:52.150 --> 36:54.350
I have business to discuss with Ms. Xia.

36:54.360 --> 36:54.760
Okay.

36:58.880 --> 37:00.440
Thank you for coming. Come on,

37:00.440 --> 37:01.100
please sit.

37:02.630 --> 37:03.230
Everyone,

37:03.840 --> 37:04.400
you should all

37:04.400 --> 37:06.190
know Ms. Xia by now.

37:07.960 --> 37:08.550
How about this?

37:08.550 --> 37:09.190
Daughter,

37:09.630 --> 37:10.690
you must remember,

37:11.030 --> 37:13.160
a woman must have a sense of propriety.

37:13.360 --> 37:14.800
Never act so willfully.

37:14.920 --> 37:16.970
This is very important for a woman.

37:17.000 --> 37:17.960
Do you understand?

37:17.960 --> 37:18.400
Mommy,

37:18.920 --> 37:21.250
don't talk to my little sister about this.

37:21.550 --> 37:22.280
Stepmother,

37:22.440 --> 37:23.300
don't be angry.

37:23.800 --> 37:24.480
Be careful

37:24.870 --> 37:26.000
not to harm the baby.

37:29.440 --> 37:30.370
How did you know?

37:31.440 --> 37:31.840
You keep

37:31.840 --> 37:33.110
covering your belly with your hand.

37:33.110 --> 37:34.170
Who wouldn't know?

37:37.690 --> 37:39.440
We have a saying here.

37:39.920 --> 37:41.360
Before the third month of pregnancy,

37:41.360 --> 37:42.880
you must not announce it.

37:43.190 --> 37:43.850
Otherwise,

37:44.070 --> 37:45.330
there will be bad luck.

37:46.350 --> 37:47.610
You need to be careful.

37:48.400 --> 37:49.030
Vivi,

37:49.670 --> 37:51.350
you're quite new here with Mr. Du,

37:51.350 --> 37:52.950
so you don't know some rules.

37:52.960 --> 37:55.030
There are some spotlights you can take.

37:55.030 --> 37:56.190
Making the headlines one day

37:56.190 --> 37:57.850
and receiving gifts the next,

37:58.280 --> 37:58.920
we've all

37:58.920 --> 38:00.920
enjoyed such glamour before.

38:01.760 --> 38:03.590
But when Mr. Du talks business,

38:04.320 --> 38:06.590
you must learn
to act tactfully and properly.

38:06.590 --> 38:07.960
Mr. Du's friends are

38:08.840 --> 38:10.630
not for us to entertain.

38:11.760 --> 38:13.200
Keying is right.

38:13.760 --> 38:15.190
Ms. Xia is

38:15.550 --> 38:17.150
a rising star in real estate.

38:17.480 --> 38:19.480
The Master really appreciates her.

38:19.630 --> 38:20.710
That's why he specially

38:20.710 --> 38:22.320
invited her to this dinner today

38:22.320 --> 38:23.920
and even arranged for her
to sit at the main table.

38:23.920 --> 38:25.920
She is not someone we can compare to.

38:26.480 --> 38:28.480
A woman must have a clear understanding

38:28.480 --> 38:29.800
of her own position.

38:37.150 --> 38:39.070
The Golden Sands Pool in Shengcheng is

38:39.070 --> 38:40.600
your masterpiece, Ms. Xia.

38:41.230 --> 38:43.100
When Luna Clothing launched,

38:43.550 --> 38:45.760
you even beat the designer who came back

38:46.190 --> 38:47.400
from America.

38:48.030 --> 38:49.480
In the near future, Gangdao

38:49.480 --> 38:50.840
will return to the homeland.

38:50.840 --> 38:51.680
Chengrong

38:51.710 --> 38:55.400
will definitely enter Shengcheng
to develop.

38:56.400 --> 38:57.600
When that time comes,

38:58.800 --> 38:59.510
Ms. Xia,

39:00.070 --> 39:01.280
we must continue

39:01.280 --> 39:02.810
our pleasant cooperation.

39:03.440 --> 39:04.170
Chairman Du,

39:04.480 --> 39:06.190
thank you for your compliments.

39:06.190 --> 39:06.880
But I am just

39:06.880 --> 39:09.090
a consultant
for Chengrong Electronics City.

39:09.090 --> 39:10.710
As for the cooperation
with Chengrong Group,

39:10.710 --> 39:12.040
I wouldn't call it that.

39:16.480 --> 39:18.140
There is plenty of time ahead!

39:38.760 --> 39:39.490
He is inside.

39:39.570 --> 39:40.190
Follow me.

39:40.550 --> 39:41.030
Okay.

39:57.510 --> 39:58.230
I am so glad

39:58.510 --> 40:00.640
that everyone is gathered here today.

40:10.320 --> 40:11.980
Actually, there is something

40:12.480 --> 40:13.440
that is no longer a secret.

40:13.440 --> 40:15.360
I believe many of you know about it.

40:15.360 --> 40:17.230
Around this time last year,

40:17.360 --> 40:18.620
I called my two sons,

40:18.800 --> 40:19.930
Zhaohui and Zhaoji,

40:20.070 --> 40:21.070
to my study

40:21.280 --> 40:23.280
and gave each of them a check

40:23.580 --> 40:25.830
for 20 million Gangdao dollars.

40:26.670 --> 40:28.480
Whoever, within one year,

40:28.670 --> 40:30.440
achieves greater success

40:30.820 --> 40:31.760
and greater development

40:31.760 --> 40:33.590
will be awarded with 5%

40:33.590 --> 40:35.190
of Chengrong Group's shares

40:35.230 --> 40:36.480
by me.

40:47.400 --> 40:48.000
Come out.

40:50.320 --> 40:51.920
It's me, Pan Baohua.

40:53.960 --> 40:54.630
Mr. Xiao,

40:55.190 --> 40:56.120
you can come out.

40:56.670 --> 40:57.320
It's me.

40:59.190 --> 41:00.630
It's me, Pan Baohua.

41:04.320 --> 41:05.550
Over here. Here.

41:17.670 --> 41:19.130
When can I go back with you?

41:19.670 --> 41:20.400
We came today

41:20.510 --> 41:21.710
just to take you back.

41:22.320 --> 41:22.920
Was it him?

41:28.050 --> 41:29.160
Did you see him

41:29.190 --> 41:30.450
on the day of the crime?

41:32.070 --> 41:33.280
This person disappeared

41:33.280 --> 41:34.140
after that day.

41:39.840 --> 41:40.800
The temporary worker,

41:40.800 --> 41:42.400
Wang Qiang, died in Nanyang.

41:42.670 --> 41:43.510
It was this man who got him

41:43.510 --> 41:45.110
into the construction site.

41:45.150 --> 41:45.750
His name is

41:46.710 --> 41:47.570
Xiao Jianyong.

42:07.110 --> 42:07.970
Xiao Jianyong.

42:09.630 --> 42:11.160
Do you remember Wang Qiang?

42:12.920 --> 42:14.180
I don't know anything!

42:15.280 --> 42:16.360
Construction sites

42:16.360 --> 42:18.030
see so many people coming and going.

42:18.030 --> 42:19.360
Sometimes when work is urgent,

42:19.360 --> 42:21.090
it's normal to hire a few temps!

42:21.360 --> 42:22.230
I was careless

42:22.710 --> 42:24.510
and didn't check IDs carefully.

42:24.560 --> 42:25.820
But I really had no idea

42:25.880 --> 42:27.080
about anything else.

42:28.480 --> 42:29.610
After the incident,

42:29.630 --> 42:31.030
someone found me and said

42:31.230 --> 42:32.360
I was in big trouble.

42:32.750 --> 42:33.740
I was scared.

42:35.760 --> 42:36.690
That person said

42:36.840 --> 42:38.480
he'd bring me to Gangdao
to make a fortune.

42:38.480 --> 42:39.320
But it turned out

42:39.320 --> 42:40.360
to be smuggling.

42:41.320 --> 42:42.380
I wanted to go back,

42:42.510 --> 42:43.370
but I couldn't.

42:45.230 --> 42:46.160
Calm down first.

42:46.800 --> 42:47.930
We can take you back.

42:48.150 --> 42:49.750
But I need your cooperation.

42:49.800 --> 42:50.400
After we go back,

42:50.400 --> 42:51.670
tell the police everything

42:51.670 --> 42:53.000
you know. Can you?

42:54.030 --> 42:54.960
I'll cooperate.

42:55.110 --> 42:56.310
I can testify for you.

42:56.590 --> 42:57.720
It was Liu Tianquan!

42:58.400 --> 42:59.200
Wang Qiang was

42:59.320 --> 43:00.450
Liu Tianquan's man.

43:00.590 --> 43:01.520
Liu Tianquan is

43:01.550 --> 43:02.480
a jerk!

43:03.710 --> 43:05.170
Wang Qiang worked for him,

43:05.190 --> 43:06.050
but he sent Wang

43:06.270 --> 43:07.930
to Nanyang and had him killed.

43:08.590 --> 43:09.390
If I stay here,

43:10.130 --> 43:11.660
I'll be the next Wang Qiang.

43:11.880 --> 43:13.080
I'll go back with you.

43:13.550 --> 43:14.550
None of my two sons

43:14.710 --> 43:15.920
disappointed me.

43:16.860 --> 43:18.980
The factory in Thailand

43:19.030 --> 43:22.230
and the Electronics City in Shengcheng are

43:22.840 --> 43:23.920
both great successes.

43:23.920 --> 43:25.710
Any one of them could be

43:26.110 --> 43:27.970
considered a brilliant project.

43:29.000 --> 43:29.880
So, Zhaohui,

43:30.110 --> 43:31.480
I am very satisfied with everything

43:31.480 --> 43:32.320
you've done.

43:33.630 --> 43:35.290
Then let's talk about Zhaoji.

43:35.550 --> 43:36.880
He is good at both studying

43:36.880 --> 43:38.230
and doing business.

43:38.710 --> 43:39.550
So, Zhaoji,

43:40.150 --> 43:42.010
I'm happy for you and proud of you.

43:48.400 --> 43:49.590
Both are my sons,

43:49.920 --> 43:51.380
and both have done so well.

43:51.680 --> 43:53.850
So, who should be rewarded

43:53.880 --> 43:54.890
with the 5%

43:54.920 --> 43:56.180
of the group's shares?

44:01.110 --> 44:01.840
Chairman Du,

44:02.000 --> 44:03.760
don't keep us in suspense.

44:03.930 --> 44:04.600
Yeah, Chairman Du.

44:04.600 --> 44:05.660
Who would win them?

44:05.890 --> 44:07.240
Could it be a tie?

44:08.630 --> 44:09.960
Since it's a competition,

44:09.960 --> 44:11.820
there must be a winner and a loser.

44:11.920 --> 44:13.050
How could it be a tie?

44:26.330 --> 44:27.530
You can't leave yet.

44:30.190 --> 44:30.790
Don't run.

44:31.620 --> 44:32.820
You'll die if you run.

44:56.090 --> 44:57.020
Let's go. Hurry.

44:58.510 --> 44:59.150
Move it.

45:00.440 --> 45:01.840
Five percent

45:01.840 --> 45:03.640
of the Chengrong Group's shares

45:03.800 --> 45:04.230
go

45:05.800 --> 45:06.470
to Zhao...
